But it is essential that we ask ourselves: what are we willing to give up to achieve that dream? #NigeriaDecides2023

Yet, the mark of a great nation is not just its ability to endure but its capacity for resilience and perseverance. We cannot expect to achieve greatness while simultaneously clinging to our comfort and convenience. #NigeriaDecides2023

Similarly, when we are wronged, we often get counsel from people around us to not seek justice, to just let it go and "not burn bridges".

Yet, the mark of a great nation is not just its ability to endure but its capacity for resilience and perseverance. #NigeriaDecides2023

Consider, for instance, if our nation were being invaded the way Ukraine has been by Russia for this long. I fear that many Nigerians in the name of peace, would protest for the president to give up rather than stand up for what is right. #NigeriaDecides2023
